A A new remedy has been discovered and tested
for easing unwanted behaviour in patients with
Tourette’s syndrome.
B Conventional drugs in combination with psychological treatment might have an effect on
patients with Tourette’s syndrome.
C Dopamine has been found to help patients with
Tourette’s syndrome.
D Habits seem to play only a minor role for
patients with Tourette’s syndrome.
